Description:
Legal Advice and Consulting Services

I will offer sound legal advice and consulting services, the full spectrum will be on business matters. They will include:

* Business Plans;
* Legal Opinion;
* Legal Drafting;;
* Capital structures;
* Shareholder meetings;
* Commercial contracts;
* Dissolution and liquidation;
* Employment policy;
* Non-competition and non-disclosure agreement;
* Regulatory compliance;
* Contracts and compensation; and
* Debt and Equity financing and investment

**Why this Gig is good for you**

The gig will seek to exploit all the legal provisions which will articulate the task in hand. The potential clients are guaranteed quality and professional, advise tailor-made to address their legal situation.

**Guarantees**

Timely delivery;

Quality Work; and

Original work

**Note: Kindly reach me before placing your order, this will aid in getting the relevant requirements and also advise you on the best approach to be undertaken. Thank you as you consider the gig and I look forward to working with you.**
